-- Onex, CPPIB to sell Gates Corp to Blackstone for $5.4 bln
-- 
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 04:48PM EDT
-- None



April 4 (Reuters) - Onex Corp <OCX.TO> and Canada Pension Plan Investment Board (CPPIB) said they would sell Gates Corp to private equity firm Blackstone Group LP <BX.N> for $5.4 billion.

Gates is a division of Tomkins, which Onex and CPPIB jointly bought in 2010 for about $5 billion. [ID:nMKWQ8qNGa]